fields.name: Black Forest Cake
fields.description: Several layers of chocolate cake, with cherry filling, with lashings of whipped cream between each layer. The cake is then decorated with piped, whipped cream, maraschino cherries, and chocolate shavings.

fields.name: Mango Fruit Cake
fields.description: [Eggless]. Bite into SweetBackery's artisanal Mango fruit cake topped with tasty mangoes and our fresh cream made right after the order is placed.

All our cakes are made fresh and with love, with no added preservatives, all-natural, and best-quality ingredients safe for children and adults.
